TextEng: "Goodbye."
"Vix'thra is no more. Leave it at that."
"Mind your words or I'll kill you, too."
"Yes, I destroyed Vix'thra. You're all free now."
Text: "그래, 내가 빅스트라를 파괴했어. 너희 모두 이제 자유야."

TextEng: "Look, I did my part. High Priest Sodalis is yours to deal with."
Text: "봐, 내 몫은 했어. 대사제 소달리스는 네가 처리해."

TextEng: "And it serves you right. What good have you done me, anyway?"
Text: "자업자득이야. 어차피 넌 내게 뭘 해준 것도 없잖아?"

TextEng: "If blood will be spilled, it will be that of High Priest Sodalis."
"Goodbye."
"The High Priest is dead. Leave it at that."
"Hmph. I did it for my reasons, not yours."
Text: "흥. 내 이유로 한 거지, 네 이유가 아니야."

TextEng: "Yes, Drearing's Deep is free now."
"Look, I did my part. Vix'thra's yours to deal with."
Text: "봐, 내 몫은 했어. 빅스트라는 네가 처리해."

TextEng: "And it serves you right. What good have you done me, anyway?"
Text: "자업자득이야. 어차피 넌 내게 뭘 해준 것도 없잖아?"

TextEng: "And how do you propose I kill a god?"
"Goodbye."
"You're scared of the priests, aren't you."
"Heretic! I should turn you over to the priests myself!"
"You shouldn't speak ill of the church..."
"I think that could be arranged."
"How does a Ceremony get called?"
"Why do you say I shouldn't come here?"
"Why? What price is placed on freedom?"
"What is this place?"
"What do you mean, it claims you all?"
"You seem nervous..."
"What isn't as it seems?"
"Who are you?"
"Who enslaved you?"
"Vix'thra?"
